      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S54 platform. The naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline, with the double VANOS system recently serviced to ensure optimal cam timing and torque delivery. Power is sent through a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a limited-slip rear differential, providing excellent mechanical grip. Crucially, the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed. While the exterior shows honest wear from spirited use, the chassis remains rigid, and the suspension geometry is dialed in with refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. This is a driver-focused machine with excellent compression across all cylinders.",
      "price": 32500.0,
